    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4130816870?book_show_action=true">Jul 23, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elizabeth Danielson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elizabeth Danielson" href="/user/show/14271273-elizabeth-danielson">Elizabeth Danielson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4130816870" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer692872078004043083">I found this a fascinating read. James kept a journal for a year and this is the result. She shares snippets of her daily, reflects on British society and her history, mentions friends who are other authors I like, and writes about the craft of writing. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


